    "description": "Key Findings Ransomware in Q1 2026: Consolidation at Scale During the first quarter of 2026, we monitored more than 70 active data leak sites (DLS) that collectively listed 2,122 new victims. This figure represents a 12.2% decline from the Q4 2025 all-time record of 2,416 victims but remains the second-highest Q1 on record at 117% [&#8230;] \n The post  The State of Ransomware &#8211; Q1 2026  appeared first on  Check Point Research .",
    "source_url": "https://research.checkpoint.com/2026/the-state-of-ransomware-q1-2026/",
